 Amreesh ChandraFocuses on materials science, especially alternative energy storage with sodium-ion and supercapacitor technologies, nanostructure materials for batteries, and scalable solutions for electric vehicles
 .Debamalya BanerjeeSpecializes in graphene electronics, AC/DC transport in semiconductors, piezoelectric materials, and novel sensor devices for soil, electrical, and electrochemical applications
 .Dipak Kumar GoswamiResearches surfaces and interfaces, nanoscale science, organic electronic devices, and healthcare sensors, with notable work in organic transistors, supercapacitors, and bio-waste derived materials for energy storage
 .Jyotirmoy BhattacharyaTheoretical physics, specializing in quantum field theory, string theory, and gravity. Significant contributions to hydrodynamics from black branes, entanglement entropy, and fluid dynamics in QFTs
 .Pintu PatraWorks on active matter and theoretical biophysics, collective dynamics of biological systems, and the expansion and motility of bacterial colonies as a model for living systems
 .Poornachandra Sekhar BuradaNon-equilibrium statistical mechanics, soft matter, and fluid mechanics, focusing on Brownian motion in confined environments, chemotaxis, dynamics of self-propelled bodies, protein response to radiation, and computational physics
 .Prasanta Kumar DattaStudies laser physics, nonlinear optics, ultrafast science, and photonic materials with applications in mid-IR generation, quantum dots for solar cells, and ultrafast optical spectroscopy
 .Saikat DasEngages in experimental condensed matter physics, focusing on scanning probe microscopy, materials and microwave devices, low-temperature physics, and reliability engineering of electronic materials including Li-ion batteries
 .Samit Kumar RayExperimental condensed matter physics and nanoscience: semiconductor nanostructures, epitaxial quantum structures, nanophotonics, floating-gate flash memory, quantum dot detectors, and strained silicon for new device physics
 .Samudra RoyResearches nonlinear photonics, photonic cavity dynamics, spatial and temporal dissipative solitons, graphene-based photonic metamaterials, and waveguide arrays for optical applications
 .Shivakiran B N BhakthaInvestigates random lasers, optofluidics, photonic crystals, microresonators, glass photonics, and glass-ceramic phenomena, especially light-matter manipulation in engineered disordered systems
 .Sonjoy MajumderAtomic and molecular physics, quantum optics, ultracold atoms, quantum computing, light-matter interactions, and many-body theory in cold atomic systems
 .Tamoghna DasQuantum information theory, quantum optics, foundations of quantum mechanics, and quantum cryptography, including quantum correlations in communication networks and machine learning applications in quantum theory
 .Tirtha Sankar RayHigh-energy physics, astroparticle physics, and beyond the Standard Model phenomenology, focusing on composite Higgs models, dark matter models, and radiative corrections in particle theory
 .

